window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>“One leaps, one slides, one flies. One will be chosen. One will be copied. One will be lost.”</b></p> <p>Those are the words of Sybilla's prophecy. Her visions all seem to come true in one way or another. Now the lives of three young women and the destiny of a hero hang in the balance.</p> <p>But Aden doesn't believe in fate. He's determined to make his own future and with it a future for all the world.</p> <p>So far he has resisted the dictates of the board and turned down the lure of the shadow. Does he have what it takes to defy destiny, itself?</p>"; 
